{"Id":134,"LanguageCodes":["en","eng"],"Name":"eng-njdawood","Author":"N J Dawood","Language":"English","Description":"English","Direction":"ltr","Source":"","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"THE DISASTER"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"What is the Disaster"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"Would that you knew what the Disaster is"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"On that day people shall become like scattered moths"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"and the mountains like tufts of carded wool"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"Then he whose good deeds weigh heavy in the scales"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"shall live in bliss"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"but he whose good deeds are light"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"the Abyss shall be his home"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"Would that you knew what this is like"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"It is a scorching fire"}]}